text: Jean-Michel Villaumé (born March 24, 1946 in Bavilliers, Territoire de Belfort) is a member of the National Assembly of France. He represents the Haute-Saône department, and is a member of the Socialiste, radical, citoyen et divers gauche. ==References== Category:1946 births Category:Living people Category:People from the Territoire de Belfort Category:Deputies of the 13th National Assembly of the French Fifth Republic Category:Deputies of the 14th National Assembly of the French Fifth Republic
title: Jean-Michel Villaumé
